WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:00.500 align:middle line:90%


00:00:00.500 --> 00:00:03.610 align:middle line:84%
>>If you're ready for a wild
ride and a hoot to boot,

00:00:03.610 --> 00:00:05.210 align:middle line:84%
you'll love this
close-up interview

00:00:05.210 --> 00:00:06.730 align:middle line:90%
with Dannion Brinkley.

00:00:06.730 --> 00:00:09.250 align:middle line:84%
Whoever said lightning
never strikes twice

00:00:09.250 --> 00:00:11.240 align:middle line:90%
was wrong, dead wrong.

00:00:11.240 --> 00:00:12.980 align:middle line:84%
The first time lightning
struck Dannion,

00:00:12.980 --> 00:00:15.100 align:middle line:84%
he was essentially
fried and lay dead

00:00:15.100 --> 00:00:18.140 align:middle line:84%
for 28 minutes,
sheet over his face,

00:00:18.140 --> 00:00:20.220 align:middle line:84%
before returning from
an incredible journey

00:00:20.220 --> 00:00:21.510 align:middle line:90%
to the other side.

00:00:21.510 --> 00:00:24.930 align:middle line:84%
The second time, which resulted
in a near-death experience,

00:00:24.930 --> 00:00:27.280 align:middle line:84%
Dannion realized there
was a story to tell,

00:00:27.280 --> 00:00:29.170 align:middle line:84%
a story that will
ensure that anyone who

00:00:29.170 --> 00:00:32.610 align:middle line:84%
is facing transition, which
will ultimately be all of us,

00:00:32.610 --> 00:00:35.840 align:middle line:84%
will view the experience in a
much more embracing and loving

00:00:35.840 --> 00:00:36.610 align:middle line:90%
way.

00:00:36.610 --> 00:00:40.000 align:middle line:84%
For many, his story actually
takes away the fear of dying.

00:00:40.000 --> 00:00:43.395 align:middle line:10%
